<h2>New Order Received!</h2>
<p>You have a new order from <%= @order.pos? ? (@order.pos_customer_name.presence || "Walk-in Customer") : @order.user&.email %>.</p>
<p><strong>Order #:</strong> <%= @order.order_number %></p>
<p><strong>Total:</strong> Rs. <%= number_with_delimiter(@order.total) %></p>
<p>Please log in to your vendor dashboard to process this order.</p>
